---
title: Sweet Chilli-Ginger Chicken & Garlic Rice with Stir-Fry Veggies & Crispy Shallots
description: Sweet chilli ginger, it rolls off the tongue and into your belly. The spice of the ginger pops against the sweet chilli
sauce and chicken, as it soaks into the garlic rice to blend the dish together. Grab a fork full of the colourful slaw too
because how could you refuse something so pretty and tasty! Your bellies will thank you for it.
